						<summary>

						<p>On a boulder near the <hi rend="italic">Mātā-guḍi</hi> in this village.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Chaṁdrasēnadēvarāja</hi></p>						

						<p>This Hindi record in Dēvanāgarī script may be assigned on palaeographical considerations to about the 14th century.</p>						

						<p>It mentions one of the Kākaira chiefs Chaṁdrasēnadēvarāja belonging to Kākēra-mahāsthāna.</p>						

